{"tid":899411,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【封盤唔賣】尚悦．嶺即日起停售51伙","createTime":"2018-11-12T11:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T15:45:22.000Z","uid":174649,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"f5faec7bd567e057018f875a73dfe95e47ee0520","tid":899411,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181112/large/1542013571_8b82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F1542013571_8b82.jpg&h=340833bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市氣氛轉冷，恒地(012) 元朗蝶翠峰尚悦．嶺上載最新銷售安排，即日停售51伙，單位全部位處1座，實用面積195至370方呎，涉及24伙開放式、13伙1房及14伙2房。項目上周一(11月5日)首輪銷售僅沽75伙，不足首批152伙5成，開售至今累沽82伙，套現逾3.2億元。<br />\n<br />\nStrong Hold<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd34989ed8dc40adadc0ffd409c1f8e06b6b4209","tid":899411,"uid":5686,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"f5faec7bd567e057018f875a73dfe95e47ee0520","tid":899411,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181112/large/1542013571_8b82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F1542013571_8b82.jpg&h=340833bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市氣氛轉冷，恒地(012) 元朗蝶翠峰尚悦．嶺上載最新銷售安排，即日停售51伙，單位全部位處1座，實用面積195至370方呎，涉及24伙開放式、13伙1房及14伙2房。項目上周一(11月5日)首輪銷售僅沽75伙，不足首批152伙5成，開售至今累沽82伙，套現逾3.2億元。<br />\n<br />\nStrong Hold<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"餓吓啲蝗/豬，反正一定要買樓做投資/自用，hold 到佛誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c553d150080a1fd7368c75845520f8212651982","tid":899411,"uid":122377,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"發展商 重博緊樓市會反